        select {
        case <-sw.done:
            return
        case sw.result <- Event{Type: action, Object: obj}:
        }
    }
}
```

**Key data flow:** HTTP body bytes → `framer.NewFrameReader` (length-delimited frames) → `streaming.NewDecoder` (deserializes `metav1.WatchEvent`) → `restclientwatch.Decoder.Decode()` (extracts `EventType` + inner `runtime.Object`) → `StreamWatcher.receive()` goroutine → unbuffered `chan watch.Event`.

